dct_description_sm: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas Sheet 32 (1903) New Jersey Geological Survey Relief shown by 10 ft. contour interval and spot heights. Depths shown by soundings in feet at low tide. Title is not given. Region covered: southern Burlington County. Original survey1886, principal features revised 1903. From original surveys and levelings. Based on the triangulation of the U. S. Coast and Geodetic Survey.
dct_publisher_sm: Trenton, N.J. : Geological Survey of New Jersey, 1903.
Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1903.
